<br>
press ctrl<br>
press shift<br>
press 5     // This activates HotButton 5 which is /stop song<br>
delay 0.05<br>
release 5<br>
release shift<br>
release ctrl<br>
delay 0.05<br>
press Alt<br>
press 1   // To cast spell gem 1<br>
delay 0.10<br>
release 1 <br>
release Alt<br>
<br>
<br>
and no more double tapping. The songs I twist I keep in the first four hot-keys for what I twist, for easy swapping, and have the first 2 banks set up indentically for when I need to switch between a couple of twists frequently. Otherwise I just twist manually. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Brother <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=133565" target="_blank">Tyrrz</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> &lt;<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.suntzucouncil.com" target="_blank">Sun Tzu Council</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->&gt;<br>
