<br>
It doesn't interfere with the chat bar, but it will execute UI shortcuts while you are typing certain letters, in the chat bar.<br>
<br>
I found myself randomly closing the target, spell and group windows while auto-twisting and chatting, using the ALT keys.<br>
<br>
<br>
I swapped targetting (f1-f<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->    and spell casting (alt1-<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   , then rewrote my marcos.  Everything works great.<br>
