Yes, it is possible.<br>
<br>
In EverQuest go to Options, then Keyboard.<br>
Select the Casting Hotkeys. <br>
Now just change the hotkeys for spell gems 1-8 from CTRL+# to a function key or whatever. <br>
<br>
Then program your Nostromo to use those keys. If you are using function keys, you can actually have the Nostromo twisting and be chatting on the keyboard since the function keys don't send anything to the chat box. Kinda nice to be able to talk in game.  <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><br>
